rows.label: fev11_050_150_msg0001
rows.name:
Right, we've got our ingredients,
fire's nice and toasty... I think we're
all set for the night!

rows.label: fev11_050_150_msg0002
rows.name:
Shin would you mind making a start
on the cooking?

rows.label: fev11_050_150_msg0007
rows.name:
Better Shin than me. If I were in
charge I'd probably end up losing
a limb peeling the veggies!

rows.label: fev11_050_150_msg0008
rows.name:
It's not all one-sided, though. Laura
has her own talents. Like making
charms. That I could never do.

rows.label: fev11_050_150_msg0009
rows.name:
Right! We make up for each other's
strengths and weaknesses.

rows.label: fev11_050_150_msg0010
rows.name:
Blade or Driver, no one has to
shoulder all the burden.

rows.label: fev11_050_150_msg0012
rows.name:
Okay, I'm going to make a start on the
Trout Stralu. It won't take long.
